        {
            "title": "日本3月工廠產出意外下滑;零售銷售超預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BRo9vkYgHQbhPCnal5.ffA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEBB70BS_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 官方數據週四顯示,日本3月工廠產出因全球不確定性導致成本上升而意外下滑,但零售銷售增長顯示出溫和韌性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">工業生產3月環比下降0.5%,不符合市場預期的增長1.0%。此次下滑延續了2月下降2.1%的趨勢,當時需求疲軟和供應中斷打擊了產出。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於投入成本上升以及包括中東衝突在內的全球緊張局勢對市場情緒和供應鏈造成壓力,製造商仍保持謹慎態度。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">前瞻性指標顯示工廠活動將出現溫和回升。接受政府調查的製造商預計4月產出將增長2.1%,5月將增長2.2%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ad8e34f7-7a15-3553-ad8f-1c9ed1c441fa-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">零售銷售3月同比增長1.7%,超過預期的0.9%增幅,較上月下降0.1%大幅回升。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些好壞參半的數據凸顯出日本經濟動能不均,儘管外部不利因素令前景蒙上陰影,但國內需求仍保持穩定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本央行本週維持利率在0.75%不變,符合預期,但該決定顯示出日益增強的鷹派傾向。三名董事會成員投反對票支持加息,顯示對通脹壓力的擔憂日益加劇。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC3%E6%9C%88%E5%B7%A5%E5%BB%A0%E7%94%A2%E5%87%BA%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E4%B8%8B%E6%BB%91-%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E8%B6%85%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-011430826.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-30 09:30:35",
