            "title": "今日我咁睇｜美伊局勢未改善 油價高企恐慌有限 恒指料高位整固｜小編苟豪",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RjdQBY8WGYSi0QALUmXJVw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/bossmind_356/97427747e74d8bb917b02beeffff83d8\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">1.中東局勢暫時未有進展，消息指特朗普拒絕伊朗修改後的方案，市場憂慮戰事將一拖再拖，油價升至近期高位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2.不過，市場似乎已逐漸適應高油價的新常態，對油價的反應遠遠不及戰事開始的階段，美股固然維持強勢，即使是較弱的港股，亦未見有恐慌沽出，市場對中東戰士停火仍抱相當大的期望。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3. 恒指短期料在25800點有支持，26000點是超短線阻力，後市仍然看好，博26500點，5月有機會見27000點。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">4.選股方面，Minimax、智譜等AI大模型股仍在近月低位，可考慮入貨。藍籌股不妨考慮中資金融股，包括內銀、內險及券商。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">5. 恒指牛熊證街貨比例，牛證比例仍然較多，但又未至於重牛，因此估計整固為主。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E6%88%91%E5%92%81%E7%9D%87-%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E5%B1%80%E5%8B%A2%E6%9C%AA%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84-%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E9%AB%98%E4%BC%81%E6%81%90%E6%85%8C%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90-%E6%81%92%E6%8C%87%E6%96%99%E9%AB%98%E4%BD%8D%E6%95%B4%E5%9B%BA-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B7%A8%E8%8B%9F%E8%B1%AA-020000109.html",
